			<li>Tomoyuki Takahata, Kiyoshi Matsumoto, and Isao Shimoyama, &ldquo;Effect of Slab Deflection on a Mechano-Optic Modulator,&rdquo; <em>4th IEEE International Conference on Group IV Photonic</em>, Tokyo, Japan, 19-21 September, 2007. <strong>[<A HREF="http://dx.doi.org/10.1109/LEOS.2006.278884" TARGET="_blank">Proceedings</A>]</strong></li>
